						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 90 sheep for a perpetual lamp in the temple of Agattīśvaramuḍaiya-Mahādēva at Tiruvānāṅgūr a <hi rend="italic">brahmadēya</hi> in Tiruvaḻundūr-nāḍu on the southern bank, by a <hi rend="italic">Veḷḷāḷa</hi> resident of Pēḻaikkuḍi in Āmūr-nāḍu.</p>						

